  "3332830": {
    "name": "男神模拟器",
    "steam_appid": 3332830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/090a510885b1ad0b2d353d9ab6534daa.avif?t=1763627839\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras_big/090a510885b1ad0b2d353d9ab6534daa.avif?t=1763627839 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/d26628af68f5644d57c9c8183db20d29.avif?t=1763627839\" width=219 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一名困于现实的青年，意外穿越回学生时代，并觉醒<strong>时空恋爱战略系统</strong>。 在僚机“童锦程”的辅助下，你将跨越青涩校园与风云职场，用未来记忆改写命运，同时与七位不同人生阶段的女孩展开宿命纠缠—— <strong>从教室到写字楼，从电单车到AMG</strong>，见证她们从少女蜕变为行业翘楚，而你能否在时空交错中，找到爱情与事业的最优解？</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“江南第一深情”</strong>僚机系统 童锦程传授“雨露均沾”社交哲学：从化解修罗场到策划惊喜约会，将直接影响角色好感度演变。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/59ecb0b92605293ddc69a6b5923b9e5c.poster.avif?t=1763627839\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/59ecb0b92605293ddc69a6b5923b9e5c.webm?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/59ecb0b92605293ddc69a6b5923b9e5c.mp4?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>若琳</strong> · 总把音乐会门票夹在你课本里的青梅竹马，演奏错音时会咬嘴唇的看你。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/59951d98d66bf847161a924a487094f3.poster.avif?t=1763627839\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/59951d98d66bf847161a924a487094f3.webm?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/59951d98d66bf847161a924a487094f3.mp4?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>暖似阳</strong> · 爱吃火龙的同桌也是把创可贴拍在你手心的元气少女。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/20aec3e49578b10eedf08121ea0f4f06.poster.avif?t=1763627839\" width=614 height=345 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/20aec3e49578b10eedf08121ea0f4f06.webm?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>美羊羊 ·高冷的学生会主席 却因为做不出你爱吃的料理而默默哭泣~</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/5f80174d0590b584eb29f393f497a63e.poster.avif?t=1763627839\" width=614 height=345 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/5f80174d0590b584eb29f393f497a63e.webm?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>曲岑兮</strong> · 掌握公司命脉的商业女帝，保险柜密码是你的生日。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/af4cb164306758daa9d66cd5aec6c0f6.poster.avif?t=1763627839\" width=614 height=345 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/af4cb164306758daa9d66cd5aec6c0f6.webm?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >富老师 · 人气歌手巡演的后台总为你留VIP座位，麦克风刻着「给第一个听众」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/7c04dee7ff48ff5b75a8269129958925.poster.avif?t=1763627839\" width=614 height=345 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/7c04dee7ff48ff5b75a8269129958925.webm?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宗蕊 璀璨女明星 红毯上挽着你的手怒怼记者：「他不是金主，是我的光。」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/760fa8e9521701ae8c7389626f9fdd2b.poster.avif?t=1763627839\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/760fa8e9521701ae8c7389626f9fdd2b.webm?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/760fa8e9521701ae8c7389626f9fdd2b.mp4?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蔓越莓 能黑入对手商业大楼的超级助理，电脑桌面是你高中毕业照。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/785b0ea7c019d6fce6af30a0f87a0d8f.poster.avif?t=1763627839\" width=614 height=345 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/785b0ea7c019d6fce6af30a0f87a0d8f.webm?t=1763627839\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是刚入职网红经纪公司的新人，因一次意外被“江南第一深情”童锦程选中，成为关门弟子！在“祖师爷级”僚机的指导下，你可以同时攻略七位风格迥异的女主：从校园到娱乐圈，从青涩初恋到热辣暧昧，每一次选择都可能触发心跳暴击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/3d859ecf80d92771426ad20d86f16df5.avif?t=1763627839\" width=265 height=70 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>亲爱的玩家：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 我们是第十艺术团队，一群在互动影游领域蹒跚学步的人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一年前，《我为情狂》的失利让我们清醒：自以为是的“爆点”堆砌，抵不过一句真诚的对话；年初的《夏日盛宴》意外被认可，才让我们隐约触摸到——或许玩家真正需要的，不是完美无瑕的乌托邦，而是裂缝中透出的那缕真实的光。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于过去：</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们曾以为“大制作+顶流演员”是成功密码，直到《我为情狂》的差评如潮水般涌来：“剧情像AI生成的豪门八卦”“角色还不如NPC生动”。那段时间，办公室外最常听见的话是“要不转行吧”。 后来《夏日盛宴》立项时，我们只剩够租10天海边民宿的预算，编剧蹲在沙滩上改了三版结局，为了拍打戏全组人都倾巢出动当配角。没想到，正是这种“破釜沉舟”的笨拙，让玩家记住了李雷和那四个姑娘。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于现在：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 《男神模拟器》是我们第一次尝试时空穿越题材——毕竟连办公室WiFi都时常穿越到断联状态。没有豪华拍摄团队，也没有千万级影视联动，只有多位女孩从校服到职场的多年人生。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于遗憾：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们知道游戏仍不完美： 僚机“童锦程”的台词密度可能过高，若琳的暧昧略显青涩，蔓越莓的反转或许早有玩家猜透。但这次，我们选择让瑕疵存在——就像学生时代那张没送出的贺卡，职场初期那封写废的辞职信，人生本就不是精修海报。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于未来：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 如果有幸被你选择，请把这当作一封来自时空夹缝的信： 当你在校园拾起满地的落叶，当暖似阳在操场上突然看向你的镜头，当曲岑兮最后真实的眼泪…… 那一刻，你会看见我们埋藏的私心： 所有未完成的、被嘲笑的、笨拙的浪漫，都值得被收藏。 <strong>“世界从不缺完美答案，缺的是追问的勇气。” 感谢所有包容过我们跌倒的人，更感谢愿意给《男神模拟器》一次机会的你</strong>。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第十艺术团队 敬上</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332830/extras/46979995d7595e966bed055965416596.avif?t=1763627839\" width=265 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抖音：男神模拟器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群：831458323</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B战：第十艺术官方</p>",
